{"tid":1900404,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"日本領事透露日本打算未來不再輸出口罩","createTime":"2020-02-27T07:59:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-27T08:55:54.000Z","uid":173951,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"3a3ca55801bb50454cebf1dff8b34f1fad7fe2d6","tid":1900404,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T07:59:22.000Z","msg":"行政會議成員林正財說，早前曾與日本領事館代表商討，透露日本打算不再輸出口罩。他提到，有疫情的國家都開始不再輸出口罩，相信未來要尋找口罩將會越來越困難，所以要維持本地有足夠的口罩生產線。<br />\n<br />\n對於身兼行會成員的新民黨主席葉劉淑儀表示，若行政長官林鄭月娥願意帶頭減薪，不介意跟隨，林正財回應指，他個人沒有特別建議，又指行會沒有商討過減薪安排，將交由管治團隊決定。<br />\n<br />\n被問到預算案全民派錢並沒有包括新移民，林正財表示，市民在抗疫過程中付出很多、中小企業亦面對很大打擊，派發一萬元主要是希望促進經濟，相信關愛基金，將考慮所有被遺漏的人士。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511209-20200227.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511209-20200227.htm&d=gsiGAs%2Boihw6EKwg2XwNgQwUjfZSuDKj7BL2vQxkRkA%3D&h=67f85dc8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1511209-20200227.htm&h=d3b46de7\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1511209-20200227.htm</a>"},{"pid":"be5dbad1825a68458689b611622b0d5208fa1cc3","tid":1900404,"uid":173951,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:02:40.000Z","msg":"禁運前夕"},{"pid":"f297296baa1e27130692cc081dc738d9b4ef10f3","tid":1900404,"uid":121504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"姐係國內好大獲?"},{"pid":"ff35e720a1daf2fd0e139752ce3f60554d17c6b1","tid":1900404,"uid":135211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"留番1年後奧運用把啦"},{"pid":"f92b0d07b20c13680bfda7a02cb2f2e4249dacd9","tid":1900404,"uid":6435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"f297296baa1e27130692cc081dc738d9b4ef10f3","tid":1900404,"uid":121504,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:15:04.000Z","msg":"姐係國內好大獲?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:32:13.000Z","msg":"未知大唔大鑊<br />\n但當本地人都買唔到口罩果陣<br />\n個政府再唔做野肯定比人屌死<br />\n而家已經比人屌到飛天"},{"pid":"5f3932bbd57297293eb03127a516f54fabf71260","tid":1900404,"uid":300435,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:32:51.000Z","msg":"9月參選人立刻發動及宣傳政綱,削減驚方預算,慳返果D錢派比市民<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/fdtdPS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/fdtdPS</a><br />\n<br />\n既然777無恥派錢,<br />\n我地都可以<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />,<br />\n<br />\n依家即刻宣傳政綱,<br />\n9月立會一過半,<br />\n就即刻發動議案,<br />\n削減驚方預算，<br />\n<br />\n驚方1年預算258億元,<br />\n削減一半就130億元,<br />\n4年立法任期就520億元,<br />\n再叫政府比D錢來,<br />\n就儲夠710億,<br />\n下年又可以派一萬<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0306db8dd8baf0f8e6e8d4fb3a74a8073d23d6c","tid":1900404,"uid":2656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:41:58.000Z","msg":"strong hold口罩"},{"pid":"70dc20f51ed3c99e9231d0f2cdf3ce6ec9dc87ff","tid":1900404,"uid":267880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff35e720a1daf2fd0e139752ce3f60554d17c6b1","tid":1900404,"uid":135211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"留番1年後奧運用把啦"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:55:27.000Z","msg":"無1年後呀 過幾個月就係<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f8dd272d973142ac6b255738bcb56217914ba548","tid":1900404,"uid":135211,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"70dc20f51ed3c99e9231d0f2cdf3ce6ec9dc87ff","tid":1900404,"uid":267880,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"ff35e720a1daf2fd0e139752ce3f60554d17c6b1","tid":1900404,"uid":135211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-27T08:29:49.000Z","msg":"留番1年後